1972;;Heat;;American;;Paul Morrissey;;Joe Dallesandro, Sylvia Miles;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heat_(1972_film);;Joey Davis is an unemployed former child star who supports himself as a hustler in Los Angeles. Joey uses sex to get his landlady to reduce his rent, then seduces Sally Todd, a former Hollywood starlet. Sally tries to help Joey revive his career but her status as a mediocre ex-actress proves to be quite useless. Sally's psychotic daughter, Jessica, further complicates the relationship between Sally and the cynical, emotionally numb Joey.